<h2 id="step-4-moisturize">Step 4: Moisturize:</h2>
<p>Moisturizing is very crucial for people with oily skin. There is some weird myth that if you have oily skin, you don’t need to or shouldn’t moisturize, which is completely wrong.</p>

<p>All skin types need moisturizer, but if you have oily skin, you should be more careful with what kind of moisturizer you’re using.</p>

<p>While choosing a moisturizer for oily skin, make sure:</p>

<ul>
  <li>It is lightweight,</li>
  <li>free of oil,</li>
  <li>water-based and</li>
  <li>absorbs easily.</li>
</ul>

