<p>These are the four-step skin care routine you can use in the morning and evening to keep your skin healthy, clear, and grease-free. Once, you’re done with these steps, all you need to do is add an SPF as the last step of morning skin care routine.</p>

<h2 id="step-5-spf-am-only">Step 5: SPF (AM Only)</h2>
<p>This is the final step of skin care routine for oily skin. You should always a broad spectrum SPF every day right before you apply your makeup or heading outdoors.</p>

